# Change History

This topic provides an example of the Change History, detailing the automatic generation of a Revert Order after reverting an order.

The following is an example of the Change History. After you revert the order O-00000637, a Revert Order O-00000638 is automatically generated, including the Revert Order order action performed on O-00000637.
